description: External methods allow for interoperability between native and managed code. The newer version of Chrome also brings new settings and security updates, but some older settings may no longer be available. With the updated Chromium, the output PDF may differ from previous versions.
releaseNotes: Latest version of Chrome renderer for IronPdf on Windows x64 and Windows x86.
summary: This package contains an updated Chrome version of platform-specific native dependencies for use with the IronPdf C# PDF Library. https://ironpdf.com
title: IronPdf.Native.UpdatedChrome.Windows
